2. The Second Chapter
21. Beginning With the Uneducated
At Sāvatthī.
“Mendicants, sentient beings come together and converge because of an element:
the uneducated with the uneducated …
lazy …
witless …
learned...

uneducated …
unmindful …
witless …
learned...
mindful... wise...”

